room_title: Escape room "Rival’s Revenge Escape" by Vault Escape in Chicago
room_description:
You’ve been practicing for months. The game was close, and the referee took the victory away from you in the last minute. Robbed of the win by a bad call, you and your team have decided you are taking that trophy one way or another. You must work together to get into the coach’s office, get the trophy, and get out without being caught. But the coach is expecting trouble, and this might not be as easy as you think! Keep an eye out for any traps that might get in your way.

Start in the boys’ locker room and solve the puzzles along the way to get the trophy before he returns from practice in 60 minutes! Can you get the trophy in time?
